profile:
Yorkville Carpet Care was established in 1992 to fill a need for residential and commercial clients looking for superior carpet, upholstery and window treatment care by using environmentally safe and effective dry methods.

All of our cleaning systems are safe for children and pets, require very little drying time, and are recommended by all major carpet mills, quality furniture craftsmen, and high-end window treatment companies such as Hunter Douglas™.

services:
On-site carpet, upholstery and window covering cleaning. We clean the following, but are not limited to: broadloom, area rugs, stair runners, sofas, love seats, arm chairs, dining chairs, outdoor furniture cushions, blinds, drapes, venetians, floor grouts. 
We clean a variety of upholstery fabrics, including leather. Any type of window covering fabric in any configuration can be cleaned right where it hangs. We also apply fabric and carpet PROTECTION systems.

profile:
Finest Window Treatments in Bozeman, Montana from The Blind Guy
WE HAVE A WIDE SELECTION OF BLINDS, DRAPES, AND WINDOW TREATMENTS
Looking for custom window coverings and awnings that will brighten up or darken your home, making you the talk of the town? Look no further than The Blind Guy of Bozeman, MT. For over 18 years, The Blind Guy has been providing Idaho, Montana, Nebraska, North Dakota, Oregon, South Dakota, Utah, Washington and Wyoming the best quality products to give new looks to homes all around. If you’re looking for a new set of blinds, or a unique set of drapes to set your home off, contact us at (406) 585-0855.
 
FREE IN HOME ESTIMATES AND COMPETITIVE PRICING
When you’re looking for the perfect window covering solution for your home, the look and quality stand above all other characteristics. Choosing window coverings that are too inexpensive or too expensive costs you time and money. At The Blind Guy, we provide our customers with free in home estimates and extremely competitive pricing. As you look for your window blinds, shutters, and awnings, keep us in mind, and we’ll help you make the right decision for your home! Our in-home consultations are at no cost with no obligation, and we will definitely do our best to make sure you’re satisfied every step of the way.
 
AMERICA’S BEST BRANDS WITH THE BEST SERVICE
Our ability to get the job done right the first time stands out. With every visit and install, our team will pay attention to every detail so you have the home you’ve dreamed of without any hassle. With the best brands in window coverings from Alta Window Solutions, Graber, Insolroll and Eclipse Awnings, our team understands just how to create a pleasing environment in little time. The Blind Guy makes it easy and painless to create a whole new look!
If you have any questions, please give us a call or submit a request via our site. We look forward to serving you.
